rows.name: You have no Ovah... Who are you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056102_MSG0002
rows.name: Forgive me. Extensive cranial damage has left me blind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056102_MSG0003
rows.name:
And now the...feel of the breeze caressing my skin
is...fading.[ST:wait ]
